@startuml Sequence_Responsive_UX

actor User
participant "Client" as Client
participant "Device Detection" as Device

== Page Load ==
User -> Client: Access application
Client -> Device: Detect device type
Device --> Client: Device info
Client -> Client: Load responsive layout
Client -> Client: Load mobile/tablet/desktop CSS
Client -> Client: Initialize components
Client --> User: Render responsive UI

== User Interaction ==
User -> Client: Interact with UI
Client -> Client: Show loading state
Client -> Client: Process action
Client -> Client: Update UI state
Client -> Client: Show feedback
Client --> User: Display updated UI

== Error Handling ==
User -> Client: Trigger action
Client -> Client: Action fails
Client -> Client: Show error message
Client -> Client: Handle gracefully
Client --> User: Display error state

== Offline Detection ==
Client -> Client: Check network status
alt Online
    Client -> Client: Enable features
else Offline
    Client -> Client: Show offline message
    Client -> Client: Disable online features
end

@enduml

